title: Neville Swan
text:
Neville Swan (23 January 1930 – 3 May 2012) was an <a href="Australian%20rules%20football">Australian rules football</a>er who played with <a href="Collingwood%20Football%20Club">Collingwood</a> in the <a href="Australian%20Football%20League">Victorian Football League</a> (VFL).
